
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Azure provides many data solutions as cloud service
* Ex: Relation databases, NoSQL, Object Store
* Are fully managed services
* We can also make independent or unmanaged by our own on VM, but we should control underlying
* Better to use managed service

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Mainly look for when selecting database

	1. Security
	2. Backup
	3. Availability

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Azure SQL - Managed SQL server
* Cosmos DB - Managed NoSQL database
* Azure MySQL - Managed MySQL database 
* PostgreSQL - Managed PostgreSQL

* Storage - Object Store (Main)

* Azure Redis -  Fast in-memory database and cache, good for short lived, frequently accessed data

-------------------------------------------------------------------------